George posted a picture on Instagram of Mayweather at his bed side, while LeBron James also took to Instagram to post a tribute to the Pacers player.

George was almost certain to make USA's final 12-man team for the FIBA World Cup, which begins in Spain on August 30.

But the Pacers forward is now expected to miss a large part of the 2014-15 NBA campaign, which begins in October.

